26454.name: Producer Price Indices - Annual: Barley - Producer Price Index (2004-2006 = 100) (FAO (2017))
26454.description: Indices of agricultural producer prices that measure the average annual change over time in the selling prices received by farmers (prices at the farm-gate or at the first point of sale). Annual data are provided for over 80 countries. The three categories of producer price indices available in FAOSTAT comprise: Single-item price indices, Commodity group indices and the Agriculture producer price index.
26454.datasetName: Prices: Producer Price Indices - Annual - FAO (2017)

source.name: Producer Price Indices - Annual - FAO (2017)

source.additionalInfo:
